snippet.title: #1 Valkyrie Magical Odyssey - The Elvish Forest - No commentary
snippet.description: This was one of my favorite games growing up. I decided to upload this because I couldn't find anything related to it on youtube. This game was made by a french developer called Chili Con Valley.
